Requirements Included: (noted in comments for most features, imports not noted but can clearly be seen on the top of the class files)
  Scanner Class
  Variables,
  Constants
  switch statement
  conditional operator
  using this keyword
  Inheritance
  Abstract Classes
  Encapsulation
  Method overloading
  Arrays
  Constructor
  Super Keyword
  Exception handling
  Using Java library class such as Date, Random etc
  Println, printf methods
  Static variable and Static methods
  Recursion


Requirements Extras Not Included:
  Abstract Interfaces
  Method overriding
